---
title: Smart Indian Beef Meatballs with Chickpeas and Cilantro Yogurt
description: Tender meatballs top a jumble of roasted zucchini and chickpeas. Top of each bite with some cilantro yogurt for a refreshing flavour and a bit of extra protein.

Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie and carbohydrate amounts.

